Here's a PlantUML component diagram focusing on the deployment aspect of the CodisLabs_codis architecture:

```plantuml
@startuml CodisLabs_codis

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor<<proxy>> LightBlue
    BackgroundColor<<server>> LightGreen
    BackgroundColor<<client>> LightYellow
    BackgroundColor<<management>> LightPink
}

rectangle "Client Applications" as clients {
    [Redis Client Libraries] as clientLibs
}

rectangle "Codis Proxy Layer" {
    [Codis Proxy]<<proxy>>
    [Connection Pool]
}

rectangle "Redis Server Layer" {
    [Redis Server 1]<<server>>
    [Redis Server 2]<<server>>
    [Redis Server N]<<server>>
}

rectangle "Management & Monitoring" {
    [Codis Dashboard]<<management>>
    [Codis Admin]<<management>>
    [ZooKeeper]<<management>>
}

clients --> [Codis Proxy]
[Codis Proxy] --> [Connection Pool]
[Connection Pool] --> [Redis Server 1]
[Connection Pool] --> [Redis Server 2]
[Connection Pool] --> [Redis Server N]

[Codis Dashboard] --> [Codis Proxy] : manages
[Codis Dashboard] --> [Redis Server 1] : monitors
[Codis Dashboard] --> [Redis Server 2] : monitors
[Codis Dashboard] --> [Redis Server N] : monitors
[Codis Admin] --> [Codis Dashboard] : configures
[Codis Dashboard] --> [ZooKeeper] : stores metadata

@enduml
```